">ΧΡΙΣΤΩ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"ξε\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ξε\">ΞΕ</span><span data-text=\"ἀνεπαύσατο\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ἀναπαύω\">ΑΝΕΠΑΥΣΑΤΟ</span><span data-text=\"πρὸ\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"πρό\">ΠΡΟ</span><span data-text=\"ιδ\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ιδ\">ΙΔ</span><span data-text=\"καλανδῶν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"kalendae\">ΚΑΛΑΝΔΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἰανουαρίων\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"Ianuarius\">ΙΑΝΟΥΑΡΙΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἐπὶ\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"ἐπί\">ΕΠΙ</span><span data-text=\"τῇ\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"ια\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"ια\">ΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"ὥρᾳ\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"ὤρα\">ΩΡΑ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic002932_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic002932_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic002932.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic002932-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of Ferrua 1946-47</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"line 4\">line.4: <span>Ferrua 1982-83: no.44 alternatively: ἐπ(ὶ τῇ) ια (ὑπατίᾳ); Feissel 1987: ἐπι(νεμήσεως) αʹ or ἐπι(νεμήσεως) ιαʹ</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Rouphina, rejoicing in Christ, died at 65 years of age, 14 days before the Kalends of January (19 December), at the 11th hour [or: in the 11th consulship (of Honorius); or in the 1st/11th indiction]</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The reverse of the stone was re-used for a later Latin inscription (<a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001669\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001669</a>).</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 36.0872 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 1987.0553 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282</a>  </li><li> Ferrua 1946-1947 238 no.48 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001455\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001455</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li> Ferrua 1982-1983 15 no.44 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001996\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001996</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1993 587 n.130 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001827\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001827</a>  </li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-4  35  Interlineation    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence </div>",
